They chose to come.

He listens.

BODE (CONT'D)
All three.

Another silence.

BODE (CONT'D)
Friday.

The voice on the other end speaks long enough to change his face.

BODE (CONT'D)
No.

They do not know.

He looks toward the dining room.

At the brothers preparing around Solomon's ashes.

